        </p>
      </Q>
      <Q question="What should I do if I need to change my RSVP?">
        <p class="mt-4 text-white">
          Please re-submit the <Link href="/rsvp" preventNewTab>RSVP form</Link>
           - your previous response will be updated with your new response. If
          you need to change it after Sunday 20th April, please let George and
          Izzy know as soon as possible after.
        </p>
      </Q>
      <Q question="What should I do if I have dietary restrictions?">
